 stores around the Globe. “The Launch is expected to accommodate less than 20 people but will create impact on millions of people in Nigeria, Africa and the world at large. I will be eternally grateful if you can do this for me. You are specially invited to visit play store and other Apps stores to download the SamZuga Chat App. It is available on all platforms and devices,” he stated. The Bishop also added that he plans to reward early users of this App pretty soon. Vanguard Days after the cleric launched the establishment of 1,000 businesses for women and youths through a soft loan grant in accordance with the Samzuga vision 0202-2020, Bishop Sam Zuga has also established Samzuga Empowerment Academy to train beneficiaries of the Samzuga empowerment soft loan. The empowerment academy is the first… March 5, 2020 In "News" At the recent inauguration of the newly elected National leaders of Samzuga international, Bishop Sam Zuga of House of Joy ministry, also known as Jehovah Field Marshall pleaded with Nigerians to embrace change and become agents of change in order to make the Nation a better place. March 21, 2020 In "News" Determined to fulfill his promise of rising over 100 millionaires through his Samzuga vision 0202-2020, Bishop Sam Zuga of house of joy ministry, founder of Samzuga international/empire has kicked off part of his listed projects. February 27, 2020 In "News"